{"tid":349198,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【玩死蜘蛛俠】湯賀蘭頂唔順Stan Lee電話騷擾　辭演Spider-Man？","createTime":"2017-08-06T11:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T12:48:26.000Z","uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6ccbb005e6fb2aaced004a7231a3430afcdcc7d","tid":349198,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T11:14:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/109990/-%E7%8E%A9%E6%AD%BB%E8%9C%98%E8%9B%9B%E4%BF%A0-%E6%B9%AF%E8%B3%80%E8%98%AD%E9%A0%82%E5%94%94%E9%A0%86Stan-Lee%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1%E9%A8%B7%E6%93%BE-%E8%BE%AD%E6%BC%94Spider-Man-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F109990%2F-%25E7%258E%25A9%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E8%259C%2598%25E8%259B%259B%25E4%25BF%25A0-%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E8%25B3%2580%25E8%2598%25AD%25E9%25A0%2582%25E5%2594%2594%25E9%25A0%2586Stan-Lee%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A8%25B7%25E6%2593%25BE-%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E6%25BC%2594Spider-Man-&d=qmBGhWIfcDOk6vQx21bcvEjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=e4dc39c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/109990/-%E7%8E%A9%E6%AD%BB%E8%9C%98%E8%9B%9B%E4%BF%A0-%E6%B9%AF%E8%B3%80%E8%98%AD%E9%A0%82%E5%94%94%E9%A0%86Stan-Lee%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1%E9%A8%B7%E6%93%BE-%E8%BE%AD%E6%BC%94Spider-Man-</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/109990/thumbnail/9650e8326f7ed7a9419ce94ba31a9e25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F109990%2Fthumbnail%2F9650e8326f7ed7a9419ce94ba31a9e25.jpg&h=35fad00e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《蜘蛛俠：強勢回歸》全球票房大收，飾演蜘蛛俠嘅湯賀蘭（Tom Holland）亦紅到發紫，觀眾都大愛呢位21歲嘅新蜘蛛俠，雖則最近傳出佢狂追梅嬸Marisa Tomei但亦無阻粉絲期待佢下一次演出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過日前有外地網媒發布消息，指湯賀蘭被Marvel之父Stan Lee電話滋擾，而且談話內容古怪難頂，故決定唔再演蜘蛛俠咁話。喂喂！真定假㗎？唔通Spider-Man又要換人？唔好咁認真住！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/748675/xlarge/48734f492d140e06785ecc9393e7851e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F748675%2Fxlarge%2F48734f492d140e06785ecc9393e7851e.jpg&h=70fa743c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><ins>觀眾已普遍認為湯賀蘭演嘅蜘蛛俠係目前最好，如果又換人會好困擾。</ins><br />\n</strong><br />\n報道嘅內容都幾古怪，指Stan Lee不斷聯絡湯賀蘭，內容全是圍繞Uncle Ben，即係養大蜘蛛俠後來死咗嗰位Uncle Ben呢，Stan Lee話Uncle Ben死嗰陣，蜘蛛俠走近佢，應該要有條水柱由頸注入Uncle Ben個口，Uncle Ben感覺到味道好似有幾千隻動物浸死咗喺裡面咁。Stan Lee好似醉酒佬講嘢一樣非常騎呢！<br />\n<br />\n報道又話湯賀蘭因為頂唔順Stan Lee所以決定唔再接演蜘蛛俠電影，仲指Stan Lee喺facebook回應要送湯賀蘭一程。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/748677/xlarge/fc4af0d3308c42e930abe0b5e20c4ea4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F748677%2Fxlarge%2Ffc4af0d3308c42e930abe0b5e20c4ea4.jpg&h=8c57b3a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><ins>Stan Lee想像力豐富至創造到咁多英雄人物，但未至於語無輪次卦。<br />\n</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/748678/xlarge/276e047ef403bed4f59880b2ce3622da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F748678%2Fxlarge%2F276e047ef403bed4f59880b2ce3622da.jpg&h=779ade62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n報道更「轉載」Stan Lee的社交網頁，聲稱佢同湯賀蘭say goodbye，但我哋查過呢段貼文可能係假。<br />\n<br />\n有網友睇完好擔心蜘蛛俠又要換人，不過湯賀蘭嘅Twitter同ig都冇對事件作出回應，佢只係如常咁出席宣傳活動，而喺Stan Lee嘅facebook page亦唔見報道所轉載嘅Stan Lee回應，加上內容古怪難明，相信呢單新聞只係惡作劇啫！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/748680/xlarge/bd1d1032db78c92d8a986b6679a51985.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F748680%2Fxlarge%2Fbd1d1032db78c92d8a986b6679a51985.jpg&h=1148eab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><ins>湯賀蘭會喺《復仇者聯盟3》繼續演蜘蛛俠。</ins></strong>"},{"pid":"8bc03c6bc4fb128f759533179c3016c3e4062f30","tid":349198,"uid":183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T11:16:27.000Z","msg":"有咩可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0496247c010afe5ef22f3198d017868466407344","tid":349198,"uid":61279,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:46:53.000Z","msg":"01又出垃圾文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b64c598a3dbf71751a901420081257998f25d74","tid":349198,"uid":48791,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:48:26.000Z","msg":"on9垃圾文"}]}